LINDA: Look what I found.

1044
00:58:04,067 --> 00:58:05,193
BRADLEY: Green bananas?

1045
00:58:05,528 --> 00:58:06,779
Not for long.

1046
00:58:09,823 --> 00:58:12,535
Gonna give Mother Nature
a little kick start.

1047
