- LINDA: (GROANS)
- BRADLEY: (PANTING)

1173
01:05:46,614 --> 01:05:48,824
Okay.
This'll be good till it passes.

1174
01:05:50,993 --> 01:05:52,409
It's fucking freezing.

1175
