Yeah, uh...

1194
01:07:12,199 --> 01:07:13,116
Couldn't sleep.

1195
01:07:14,242 --> 01:07:16,911
I went to camp,
and, uh, it's all gone.

1196
01:07:16,912 --> 01:07:18,705
All washed away.

1197
01:07:18,706 --> 01:07:21,541
Probably pretty stupid of me
to build so close to shore.

1198
01:07:21,542 --> 01:07:22,459
No, it's okay.

1199
01:07:23,043 --> 01:07:24,002
Build a new one.

1200
01:07:26,046 --> 01:07:26,879
Yeah.

1201
01:07:26,880 --> 01:07:28,591
Do it on higher ground
this time, right?

1202
01:07:29,132 --> 01:07:30,132
Yeah.

1203
01:07:30,133 --> 01:07:31,134
And I can help.

1204
01:07:31,552 --> 01:07:33,929
I mean, getting stronger.

1205
01:07:35,263 --> 01:07:36,348
Could do it together.

1206
01:07:39,392 --> 01:07:40,435
I'd like that.

1207
01:08:14,762 --> 01:08:15,845
You know, this would be
a lot easier

1208
